{{vgname|星风血雨|en=Sinistar: Unleashed}}是1999年的{{lang|en|[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]}}专享动作太空射击电子游戏，由马克·米恰里克和沃尔特·赖特设计并在前[[望远镜工作室|望远镜工作室]]成员组建的小型工作室{{lang|en|GameFX}}开发。项目开发从1997年开始，起初名为《源自虚无》，与[[WMS产业|威廉姆斯]]1982年推出的《[[邪恶之星|邪恶之星]]》系列无关。从{{lang|en|[[Midway|Midway Games]]}}获得系列授权后，{{lang|en|GameFX}}调整游戏重点，开发成《邪恶之星》的续作。

与前作一样，《星风血雨》的游戏目标是摧毁通过斯波格采矿机提供能量传送出来的大型生物机械“邪恶之星”。为达成目标，玩家可以使用多种星际飞船、道具和武器。与前作相比，新作全面采用[[三维计算机图形|三维图形]]，操控方法更多。游戏共有29关，每关都有一个邪恶之星。

《星风血雨》问世后评价褒贬不一，评论称赞开发者的胆识和游戏中增加的新功能。多篇文章认为{{lang|en|GameFX}}准确把握前作代表元素，忠于系列，令粉丝倍感熟悉。但也有评论认为关卡头目设计不佳，游戏玩法太过重复。

== 游戏玩法 ==
[[File:Sinistar_Unleashed_screenshot.jpg|thumbnail]]]]

《星风血雨》与《邪恶之星》（{{lang|en|''Sinistar''}}）同属动作太空射击电子游戏，不过原作的图形和操作都局限在[[二维计算机图形|二维空间]]范围，续作拥有[[三维计算机图形|三维图形]]，所以玩家可以在六条轴线范围内自由移动。《星风血雨》共有29[[关卡_(电子游戏)|关]]，其中五个隐藏关卡，每关都要对抗邪恶之星。奖励关卡属于限时任务，玩家需摧毁或保卫特定目标。<ref name="GameSpot Review">{{cite web | last = Wolpaw | first = Erick | date = 1999-10-06 | title = Sinistar: Unleashed Review | work = GameSpot | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190521203831/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/sinistar-unleashed-review/1900-2533058/ | url = https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/sinistar-unleashed-review/1900-2533058/ | accessdate = 2020-07-05 | archivedate = 2019-05-21 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>

玩家操纵星际飞船对抗名为邪恶抽取者的外星种族及其奴隶斯波格。斯波格是邪恶抽取者控制的采矿船，负责为传送通道提供能量，通道能够传送以摧毁玩家飞船为目标的巨大生物机械怪物“邪恶之星”。传送通道位于关卡中央，斯波格用小行星附近不定时出现的能量晶体为通道提供能源。<ref name="GameSpot Preview">{{cite web | last = Park | first = Andrew | date = 1999-06-22 | title = Sinistar: Unleashed Preview | url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/sinistar-unleashed-preview/1100-2559746/ | work = GameSpot | publisher = CBS Interactive | accessdate = 2012-09-11 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6Aap3tc3D?url=http://www.gamespot.com/sinistar-unleashed/previews/sinistar-unleashed-preview-2559746/ | archivedate = 2012-09-11 | deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref name="IGN Preview">{{cite web | last = Blevins | first = Tal | date = 1999-07-21 | title = Sinistar: Unleashed | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/1999/07/22/sinistar-unleashed-2 | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | accessdate = 2020-07-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160325170149/http://www.ign.com/articles/1999/07/22/sinistar-unleashed-2 | archivedate = 2016-03-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

玩家需尽可能防止斯波格为传送通道供能，在此期间会遇到各种敌舰来袭并保护通道。玩家可以从雷达上看到敌人位置，距离较远时为白色，很近时变成红色。玩家在斯波格完成供能前摧毁通道就能过关，否则就要击败邪恶之星。玩家有六种星际飞船可选，还有八种道具和九种武器来摧毁采矿船和邪恶之星。最强大的武器叫邪恶炸弹，设计目的就是摧毁邪恶之星，同时也可用于炸毁传送通道。玩家可以像斯波格一样从小行星附近收集能量晶体来获得邪恶炸弹。<ref name="GameSpot Preview" /><ref name="IGN Preview" />

== 开发 ==
1997年，前[[望远镜工作室|望远镜工作室]]（{{lang|en|Looking Glass Studios}}）成员组建的小型[[游戏开发者|电子游戏开发商]]{{lang|en|GameFX}}开始开发《源自虚无》（{{lang|en|''Out of the Void''}}）<ref name="NGen31">{{cite magazine | title = NG Alphas: Out of the Void | magazine = Next Generation | issue = 31 | publisher = Imagine Media | date = 1997-07 | pages = 69-70 | url = https://archive.org/details/NEXT_Generation_31/page/n70 | accessdate = 2020-07-05}}</ref><ref name="AGH">{{cite web | title = AGH Preview – Sinistar: Unleashed | archivedate = 2017-03-29 | url = http://www.atarihq.com/features/sinistar/ | work = Atari Gaming Headquarters | accessdate = 2020-07-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170329195039/http://www.atarihq.com/features/sinistar/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。根据初始设计，游戏的最低配置要求为[[奔腾|奔腾]]MMX 200和[[3dfx_Interactive|3dfx]]图形加速卡，这样的硬件需求已经超出当时普通消费者的承受能力<ref name="NGen31" />。{{lang|en|3dfx}}意识到这款游戏可以很好地宣传自家图形芯片，所以与{{lang|en|GameFX}}合作支持开发<ref name="NGen31" />。《源自虚无》起初与《邪恶之星》系列没有任何关联，游戏玩法也没有类似之处，但{{lang|en|GameFX}}这年获得系列授权后决定改变新作的开发方向，与《邪恶之星》联系起来。最终游戏的图形结构不变，但加入许多与《邪恶之星》类似的特征<ref name="AGH" />。

[[THQ游戏公司|THQ游戏公司]]透露，游戏已针对当时最新发布的[[英特尔|英特尔]][[奔腾III|奔腾III]]处理器优化<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140221162813/http://news.cnet.com/Intel-touts-Pentium-III-enhancements/2100-1001_3-221788.html | last = Kanellos | first = Michael | title = Intel touts Pentium III enhancements | deadurl = no | url = https://www.cnet.com/news/intel-touts-pentium-iii-enhancements/ | work = [[CNET|CNet]] | accessdate = 2020-07-05 | date = 1999-02-17 | archivedate =2014-02-21}}</ref>，能让光线和几何变换引擎以更快速度处理更多细节<ref>{{cite web | last = Calabasas | first = Calif | title = THQ Sends Arcade Cult-Classic, "Sinistar: Unleashed" to PC; New Game Takes Advantage of Intel Pentium III Processor Capabilities | url = http://www.thefreelibrary.com/-a053896251 | work = [[美国商业信息|Business Wire]] | accessdate = 2016-03-05 | date = 1999-02-17 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305154854/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/-a053896251 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。马克·钱伯斯（{{lang|en|Mark L. Chambers}}）和罗伯·史密斯（{{lang|en|Rob Smith}}）在著作《电脑游戏玩家圣经》（{{lang|en|''Computer Gamer's Bible''}}）上称赞《星风血雨》的技术设计：“开发人员加入精确的碰撞物理特效，在小行星领域采矿需要精准的时机和灵活的手指”<ref>{{cite book | title = Computer Gamer's Bible | year = 2000 | publisher = John Wiley & Sons | isbn = 9780764533730 | page = 510 | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=Zy9mQ0HCkDcC&redir_esc=y | author1 = Mark L. Chambers | author2 = Rob Smith | accessdate = 2020-07-05 | archive-date = 2020-12-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201224064410/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=Zy9mQ0HCkDcC&redir_esc=y | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 发行 ==
{{lang|en|[[Midway|Midway Games]]}}获得《邪恶之星》系列授权两年后，{{lang|en|THQ}}游戏公司终于在1999年2月宣布推出《星风血雨》的计划<ref>{{cite web | date = 1999-02-03 | title = Sinistar Headed to PC | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/1999/02/04/sinistar-headed-to-pc | work = IGN | accessdate = 2020-07-05 | archiveurl = https://archive.vn/20130126024555/http://www.ign.com/articles/1999/02/04/sinistar-headed-to-pc | archivedate = 2013-01-26 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。游戏共发布两段演示视频，其中第二段于1999年9月问世，与第一段相比增加游戏玩法和技术改进，并演示前两关<ref>{{cite web | last = IGN Staff | date = 1999-09-16 | title = New Sinistar: Unleashed Demo, er, Unleashed | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/1999/09/17/new-sinistar-unleashed-demo-er-unleashed | work = IGN | accessdate = 2020-07-05 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6AapFRf4w?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/1999/09/17/new-sinistar-unleashed-demo-er-unleashed | archivedate = 2012-09-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

{{lang|en|THQ}}游戏公司[[首席技术官|首席技术官]]兼{{lang|en|GameFX}}总经理诺亚·戴维斯（{{lang|en|C. Noah Davis}}）在宣布游戏计划时表示，《邪恶之星》的“经典之处在于容易上手，难以精通”。他还称：“为达成同等效果，我们大量采用前作元素，同时使用专有的{{lang|en|GameFX}}技术展示其中整个宇宙。”<ref name="Press">{{cite web | last = Calabasas | first = Calif | date = 1999-02-03 | title = THQ Rockets to the PC With "Sinistar: Unleashed"; Arcade Cult Classic Enters 3-D Universe This Summer. | url = http://www.thefreelibrary.com/-a053693030 | work = Business Wire | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305135917/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/-a053693030 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | accessdate = 2016-03-05}}</ref>1999年9月3日，{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}报导游戏已[[软件版本周期|完成开发]]<ref>{{cite web | last = IGN Staff | date = 1999-09-03 | title = News Brief-let | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/1999/09/04/news-brief-let | work = IGN | accessdate = 2020-07-06 | archiveurl = https://archive.vn/20130126045022/http://www.ign.com/articles/1999/09/04/news-brief-let | archivedate = 2013-01-26 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，最终在9月15日面向全球发行<ref>{{cite  news | last = Calabasas | first = Calif | title = THQ and GameFX Ship "Sinistar: Unleashed," 3D Space Combat PC Game of Epic Proportions; Run For Cover — The Evil Sinistar is Back! | url = http://www.thefreelibrary.com/-a055748861 | work = Business Wire | accessdate = 2016-03-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305060311/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/-a055748861 | deadurl = yes | date = 1999-09-15 | archivedate = 2016-03-05}}</ref>。

